data.description: Attention investors!! This home suffered flooding from Hurricane Ian in 2022. The property holds a lot of potential for a flip, fixer upper, or new build project in a central Naples location. The home sits on almost a quarter acre of land with no homeowners association fees or rules. The workshop out back also had water damage, but is ready to be put back together and can be used as a workshop or for extra storage. You can't beat this location being only a few miles from Downtown Naples & the beaches, Gordon River Greenway & Baker Park, the new Metropolitan Naples, and all of the shopping and dining you can wish for. Property is being sold AS-IS.
